{"tid":1190243,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"Do You Hear the People Sing?","createTime":"2019-06-07T08:16:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T10:34:38.000Z","uid":82658,"like":12,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8c63ae15d5292f034f56d92001a548f8df8da124","tid":1190243,"uid":82658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T08:16:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7NOJb59.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7NOJb59.png&h=fc75bfc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LJByzjv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLJByzjv.png&h=df93eef2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T2XYLra.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT2XYLra.png&h=0eb7c32f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/huhBw6b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhuhBw6b.png&h=4b76d8e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Ha3WxS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Ha3WxS.png&h=d17f9acc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Do you hear the people sing?<br />\nSinging the songs of angry men?</span></span><br />\nIt is the music of the people<br />\nWho will not be slaves again!<br />\nWhen the beating of your heart<br />\nEchoes the beating of the drums<br />\nThere is a life about to start<br />\nWhen tomorrow comes!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gCs2sE1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgCs2sE1.png&h=22baeea3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m9MiLrH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm9MiLrH.png&h=b6166ff5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6uuDLrJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6uuDLrJ.png&h=e41a3282&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">Will you join in our <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">crusade</span>?</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Who will be strong and stand with me?</span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Somewhere beyond the barricade <br />\nIs there a world you long to see?</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">Then join in the fight<br />\nThat will give you the right to be free!</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7NOJb6W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7NOJb6W.png&h=00993189&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uyG6Ukh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuyG6Ukh.png&h=7daf21d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LEmVNFi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLEmVNFi.png&h=2764742d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/35H59TE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F35H59TE.png&h=50b5d0c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">Do you hear the people sing?<br />\nSinging the songs of angry men?</span></span><br />\nIt is the music of the people<br />\nWho will not be slaves again!<br />\nWhen the beating of your heart<br />\nEchoes the beating of the drums<br />\nThere is a life about to start<br />\nWhen tomorrow comes!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D0zsDM8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD0zsDM8.png&h=30567f26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/35jXgyP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F35jXgyP.png&h=dfc7a2dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5G2qqsa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5G2qqsa.png&h=ccf295d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">Will you give all you can give<br />\nSo that our banner may advance</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Some will <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">fall </span>and some will <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">live</span><br />\nWill you <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">stand up</span> and <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">take your chance</span>?</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">The blood of the <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">martyrs</span></strong><br />\nWill water the meadows of <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">HONGKONG</span>!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HPSaByY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHPSaByY.png&h=05d0e98a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oEVfNFD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoEVfNFD.png&h=b9c387bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E2WKF0E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE2WKF0E.png&h=eb7e2baa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0a1iLsk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0a1iLsk.png&h=34ac8dac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nDo you hear the people sing?<br />\nSinging the songs of angry men?<br />\nIt is the music of the people<br />\nWho will not be slaves again!<br />\nWhen the beating of your heart<br />\nEchoes the beating of the drums<br />\nThere is a life about to start<br />\nWhen tomorrow comes!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hn7eiNt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhn7eiNt.png&h=31387683&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1yQrUkP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1yQrUkP.png&h=f626338a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=47E2tfK5QAg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D47E2tfK5QAg&d=SmQqe2lJFulj5u2s5Cv8ui1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=8faabd3b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=47E2tfK5QAg</a>"},{"pid":"b9086cf7ed6a460bb8ad0e1c95301b7f9cecc55d","tid":1190243,"uid":82658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T08:19:26.000Z","msg":"Do you hear the people sing?"},{"pid":"b53d4803cfb2a6539fbefc405f2ad8bdbc2647ca","tid":1190243,"uid":82658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T08:19:40.000Z","msg":"Singing the songs of angry men?"},{"pid":"2582221e803decfff9bd6db6f59e9264af9ae6fa","tid":1190243,"uid":82658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T08:19:53.000Z","msg":"It is the music of the people"},{"pid":"9937b53758d69f9c1ae66ae0c9b767dcfec162bd","tid":1190243,"uid":82658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T08:20:05.000Z","msg":"Who will not be slaves again!"},{"pid":"ac88985a736a8e87131285a3a6175b99f27b1a03","tid":1190243,"uid":245101,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T08:20:15.000Z","msg":"Can't hear ."},{"pid":"b233c2062ea9cd2165bf0e1c1a77197cefc4de00","tid":1190243,"uid":82658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T08:20:18.000Z","msg":"When the beating of your heart"},{"pid":"a202ccbae35884382a6623f3b79dd83278200757","tid":1190243,"uid":82658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T08:20:34.000Z","msg