>\n你可聽見民眾的歌聲？"},{"pid":"83cf709457a4c770f945728aad314e6a9d1a3b5c","tid":1190243,"uid":82658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T08:36:45.000Z","msg":"Singing a song of angry men<br />\n唱著義憤者的歌"},{"pid":"fa4c0b8df76bca4a0e813e2bb8497ef3b81f165b","tid":1190243,"uid":82658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T08:42:51.000Z","msg":"It is the music of a people<br />\nWho will not be slaves again!<br />\n這是人民不再甘願被囚如奴隸般失去民主自由之歌！"},{"pid":"613003fa255d10bcc58c027b430dede2a7b7fc81","tid":1190243,"uid":82658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T08:46:58.000Z","msg":"When the beating of your heart<br />\nEchoes the beating of the drums<br />\n當你的心中熱血鼓動<br />\n應和著戰爭鼓聲的旋律"},{"pid":"186e7033bb2c4dd8ff532a85afe95e41f38a207b","tid":1190243,"uid":82658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T08:47:45.000Z","msg":"There is a life about to start  when tomorrow comes!<br />\n當黎明劃開天際之時便是我們浴火重生的一刻!"},{"pid":"37ec65d8ab658a9dbfacfed9383f478b8a0ac423","tid":1190243,"uid":82658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T08:50:38.000Z","msg":"Will you join in our crusade?<br />\n你會否也願加入我們的徵戰？"},{"pid":"e1c5b92e98e63639c2c7b6ff1bb54f5fc7de115b","tid":1190243,"uid":82658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T08:51:46.000Z","msg":"Who will be strong and stand with me?<br />\n堅定地與我們為伍"},{"pid":"fc4a2371aeeaddffe2b9af28c8757dabc138c161","tid":1190243,"uid":82658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T08:53:06.000Z","msg":"Beyond the barricade<br />\nIs there a world you long to see?<br />\n圍牆之外<br />\n是否就是你所渴望的一個新世界？"},{"pid":"7934c17193a26155ef3f0c687ef529844099c542","tid":1190243,"uid":82658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T08:54:03.000Z","msg":"Then join in the fight<br />\nThat will give you the right to be free!<br />\n那麼加入我們的徵戰吧<br />\n這將帶給你奔向自由的權利！"},{"pid":"504ea511380613a33c1cc9674b0b17dd503af5e0","tid":1190243,"uid":82658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T08:55:30.000Z","msg":"Will you give all you can give<br />\n你會否願意奉獻你的一切?"},{"pid":"ea814d7c9913507226baaff92174923d82acb349","tid":1190243,"uid":82658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T08:57:08.000Z","msg":"So that our banner may advance<br />\n只為我軍的旗幟可以高舉並不斷向前推進"},{"pid":"a1a3738bccdbbcf2ba8fb7f3db053eec8878f877","tid":1190243,"uid":82658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T09:03:45.000Z","msg":"Some will fall and some will live<br />\n圍牆下的雞蛋有些會抗到最後一刻然後倒下，但亦有些會在抗爭中看到生機"}]}